author: Ken Moritsugu / AP
title: China Set to End Wuhan Coronavirus Lockdown as Reported Cases Subside
description: Chinese authorities said Tuesday they will end a two-month lockdown of most of coronavirus-hit Hubei province at midnight.
content:
(BEIJING) — Chinese authorities said Tuesday they will end a two-month lockdown of most of coronavirus-hit Hubei province at midnight, as domestic cases of the virus continue to subside.
